				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "If Baelen survives the Underdark, you can talk to him in the Bonecloak Apothecary upon your arrival in LOW. He is either running the shop after harrying his wife away for the last time, or his mind is almost completely gone and he is effectively Derryth's servant."
